      <title>报道称，香港有12人因冲击立法会大楼而入狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-16/hong-kong-jails-12-for-storming-lawmakers-building-reports-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体报道，香港一家法院周六判处 12 人入狱，罪名是在 2019 年全市范围的抗议活动中冲击香港立法会大楼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-16/hong-kong-jails-12-for-storming-lawmakers-building-reports-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 06:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克着眼于减税和秋季选举——如果他能活下来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-16/sunak-eyes-tax-cuts-and-an-autumn-election-if-he-can-survive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 认为，他已准备好制定一项计划，以避免保守党在即将到来的英国大选中惨遭淘汰：9 月推出另一项减税预算，选民将在 10 月或 11 月进行投票。有机会将其付诸行动可能说起来容易做起来难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-16/sunak-eyes-tax-cuts-and-an-autumn-election-if-he-can-survive</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚石油公司寻求重写宪法以赋予议程权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-16/colombia-s-petro-seeks-rewrite-of-constitution-to-empower-agenda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚第一位左翼总统在受到这个传统保守的南美国家立法机构、法院和监管机构的阻挠后，正在寻求修改宪法，以实施他的激进议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-16/colombia-s-petro-seeks-rewrite-of-constitution-to-empower-agenda</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 02:43:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普法官对佐治亚州的裁决重启陷入僵局的选举案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-judge-s-ruling-in-georgia-restarts-stalled-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佐治亚州一名法官拒绝禁止法尼·威利斯起诉唐纳德·特朗普，这将重启她陷入僵局的选举敲诈勒索案件，但他是否会在 11 月大选前在亚特兰大接受审判却令人怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-judge-s-ruling-in-georgia-restarts-stalled-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 22:50:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国警告欧盟重启钢铁案件将导致世贸组织改革失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/us-warns-eu-that-reviving-steel-case-would-sink-wto-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国告诉欧盟，如果它在世界贸易组织就特朗普时代的钢铁和铝争端重新对华盛顿提起诉讼，那么欧盟修复多边贸易合作支柱的努力将面临着失败的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/us-warns-eu-that-reviving-steel-case-would-sink-wto-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 22:41:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西将利用二十国集团在冲突僵局中推动联合国改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/brazil-to-use-g-20-to-push-for-un-reforms-amid-conflict-deadlock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西一位高级特使表示，巴西希望利用该国今年担任 20 国集团主席国的机会，推动联合国进行改革，使该组织在解决世界冲突方面发挥更大的作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/brazil-to-use-g-20-to-push-for-un-reforms-amid-conflict-deadlock</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 22:11:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彭斯表示他不会支持特朗普重返白宫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/pence-says-he-won-t-endorse-trump-s-white-house-comeback-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前副总统迈克·彭斯表示，他不会支持共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普，这是对他的前竞选搭档的谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/pence-says-he-won-t-endorse-trump-s-white-house-comeback-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 21:22:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国因参与伊朗贸易而制裁油轮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/us-sanctions-oil-tanker-for-iranian-trade-involvement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部制裁了一艘油轮，称该油轮参与运送伊朗商品以支持胡塞叛军。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/us-sanctions-oil-tanker-for-iranian-trade-involvement</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 21:11:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在纽约的封口费审判至少推迟到四月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-march-25-hush-money-trial-in-ny-adjourned-for-30-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 因涉嫌支付封口费而在纽约举行的刑事审判原定在不到两周内开始，但被推迟了 30 天——这对这位前总统来说是一个鼓舞，他曾表示，每次拖延都会有所帮助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-march-25-hush-money-trial-in-ny-adjourned-for-30-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 20:39:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔反对党领袖敦促西非货币改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/senegal-frees-main-opposition-leader-ahead-of-march-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果塞内加尔主要反对派领导人奥斯曼·桑科(Ousmane Sonko)的联盟在本月晚些时候赢得选举，他将寻求对该地区非洲金融共同体货币进行改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/senegal-frees-main-opposition-leader-ahead-of-march-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 00:39:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
